    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I am honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. This car is in truly stunning condition\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept spotless and treated with so much love. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that looks and feels brand new without that brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. I\u2019d love for it to go to a great home where it'll be appreciated just as much as I\u2019ve enjoyed it. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
