    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated precision. Featuring the 3.8L direct-injection (DFI) flat-six, the powerplant delivers linear torque through the entire rev range, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is anchored by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring neutral handling and exceptional turn-in. This example is mechanically flawless, showing zero bore scoring and a pristine undercarriage. Every bushing, seal, and heat shield remains in concours-level condition, offering a visceral, analog driving experience that modern electronically-assisted racks cannot replicate. A truly impeccable specimen for the discerning purist.",
